    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的。adsys先向adcon发起fetch GPOs，然后adcon返回relevant GPOs resolved给adsys。最后adsys把解析后的策略应用回adcli。注意第一步还有用户认证。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "authenticate user",
