      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加。现在adsys到adcon是fetch GPOs，adcon回adsys是relevant GPOs resolved。最后一条是adsys到adcli的parse GPOs and apply，对吗？",
